nodes.text: Now, now, Terje...ever been to Texas?

Actually no. And I'd really want to go for the music. This is a quote from Bob Brozman, a great slide player that I've seen a few times. Funny guy.  The full quote is like this: 'I'm so glad to be here in Europe where you still have freedom of speech. They've taken that away from us. Remember that I come from a coutry where 40% of the people don't believe in evolution. And if you ever go to Texas... there's no evidence of any!'
Way wrong... is it wishful thinking that makes you make this assumption? :)
No. I have a beautiful wife and three grown daughters - I don't wish for no more. (That's Texan for: I have no desire for more.) :p BTW - Welcome aboard emoticon_xgood
